'''异毛蟹属'''（學名：{{lang|la|''Heteropilumnus''}}）是[[甲殼亞門|甲殼亞門]][[软甲纲|软甲纲]]之下的一個[[属|属]]<ref name="WoRMS_204429">{{WoRMS |id=204429 |title=''Heteropilumnus'' de Man, 1895 |access-date=2020-12-23 }}</ref>。原屬[[扇蟹總科|扇蟹總科]]的[[扇蟹科|扇蟹科]]<ref name="Ng">{{cite journal|journal=[[Raffles_Bulletin_of_Zoology|Raffles Bulletin of Zoology]] |year=2008 |volume=17 |pages=1–286 |title=Systema Brachyurorum: Part I. An annotated checklist of extant Brachyuran crabs of the world |first1=Peter K. L. |last1=Ng |authorlink1=黃麒麟 |first2=Danièle |last2=Guinot |first3=Peter J. F. |last3=Davie |url=http://rmbr.nus.edu.sg/rbz/biblio/s17/s17rbz.pdf |format=[[PDF|PDF]] |deadurl=yes |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20110606061453/http://rmbr.nus.edu.sg/rbz/biblio/s17/s17rbz.pdf |archivedate=2011-06-06 }}</ref>，今屬[[毛刺蟹總科|毛刺蟹總科]][[毛刺蟹科|毛刺蟹科]][[毛刺蟹亞科|毛刺蟹亞科]]{{r|WoRMS_204429}}。
生活於[[潮間帶|潮間帶]]。

==形態特徵==
本屬物種的一大特徵為其四邊形的[[頭胸甲|頭胸甲]]，前方長有長毛<ref name="Ng et Tan 1988">{{cite journal |url=https://brill.com/view/journals/cr/54/1/article-p13_3.xml |last1=Ng |first1=Peter K. L. |authorlink1=黃麒麟 |last2=Tan |first2=Leo W. H. |year=1988 |title=The Identities of Heteropilumnus Subinteger (Lanchester, 1900) and Heteropilumnus Hirsutior (Lanchester, 1900) Stat. Nov., With Description of a New Species, Heteropilumnus Holthuisi Sp. Nov. (Decapoda, Brachyura, Pilumnidae) |journal=''[[Crustaceana|Crustaceana]]'' |volume=54 |issue=1 |publisher=Brill |location=[[莱顿|Leiden]]（[[荷蘭|荷蘭]]）|pages=13-24 |doi=10.1163/156854088X00582 |language=en,fr }}</ref>。

